1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,930
[Episode 44]

2
00:00:05,420 --> 00:00:08,020
Here, I've highlighted the key points for you.

3
00:00:09,970 --> 00:00:12,270
Acting is like pursuing someone.

4
00:00:12,470 --> 00:00:15,340
Some people think they need to talk a lot and show off.

5
00:00:15,340 --> 00:00:17,710
They think spending money is the way to win someone's heart.

6
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:20,890
But actually
it's the tiny details that matter most.

7
00:00:21,410 --> 00:00:24,100
Like noticing
what songs they enjoy.

8
00:00:24,310 --> 00:00:27,310
Whether they walk fast or slow
How they view the world.

9
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:37,030
Here, this is for you.

10
00:00:41,590 --> 00:00:43,650
Remember to eat all five food groups.

11
00:00:54,630 --> 00:00:55,630
Taji.

12
00:00:58,050 --> 00:01:00,510
Hey, what are you doing? Hey!

13
00:01:01,510 --> 00:01:03,080
Hey, don't come any closer!

14
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:15,270
Where did Fuzhi run off to today?

15
00:01:22,610 --> 00:01:24,550
Or sometimes even...

16
00:01:24,550 --> 00:01:26,490
He does things for me
quietly behind my back.

17
00:01:26,490 --> 00:01:30,130
Just pure care
without asking for anything in return.

18
00:01:37,750 --> 00:01:39,570
A relationship without intimacy.

19
00:01:39,570 --> 00:01:42,270
No one knows if it can last.

20
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:46,030
But caring for each other
is sometimes a form of happiness.

21
00:01:50,090 --> 00:01:52,610
[To Be Continued]
